       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI93104.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI93104.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Inserçăo de Movimentos Bancários                           *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI93104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6800 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6900 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01 WS-SQL-AUXILIARY.
         05 IND-NULL                       PIC S9(04) BINARY.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV9310.
       COPY COCV9311.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT6800 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6800'.
           05 CON-COVT6900 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6900'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-NSALDOINI        PIC S9(17)V9(2) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NSALDOACT        PIC S9(17)V9(2) COMP-3.
           05 WS-NINTMOV          PIC 9(15) VALUE ZEROS.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME     PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI93104'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI93104         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV9310-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9310-ASE               TO COCV9311-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9310-ADE               TO COCV9311-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-VALIDACOES
                 THRU 2299-VALIDACOES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2260-UPDATE-CONTAS
                 THRU 2260-UPDATE-CONTAS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-INSERE-DADOS
                 THRU 2399-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-UPDATE-SALDO
                 THRU 2500-UPDATE-SALDO-EXIT
           END-IF.
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV9310-CTIPOMOV EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9311-CTIPOMOV-CAPLIC
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9311-CTIPOMOV-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV9311-CTIPOMOV-MSG
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV9310-DDATMOV EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV9311-DDATMOV-CAPLIC
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV9311-DDATMOV-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT   TO COCV9311-DDATMOV-MSG
              END-IF
            END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF COCV9310-DDATVAL EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO    TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC          TO COCV9311-DDATVAL-CAPLIC
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO   TO COCV9311-DDATVAL-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT   TO COCV9311-DDATVAL-MSG
              END-IF
            END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9310-GREFMOV EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9311-GREFMOV-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV9311-GREFMOV-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9311-GREFMOV-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND COCV9310-NVALORMOV EQUAL ZEROS
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV9311-NVALORMOV-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV9311-NVALORMOV-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV9311-NVALORMOV-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2250-TABELA-CONTAS
                  THRU 2250-TABELA-CONTAS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2299-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2250-TABELA-CONTAS
      *-------------------------------------------------------------
       2250-TABELA-CONTAS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2250-TABELA-CONTAS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9310-CIBAN        TO COCD6800-CIBAN.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       CIBAN
                     , CSWIFT
                     , CCONTA
                     , GDESC
                     , NINTCNT
                     , NINTMOV
                     , NSALDOINI
                     , CMOEDA
                     , NSALDOACT
                 INTO
                       :COCD6800-CIBAN
                     , :COCD6800-CSWIFT
                     , :COCD6800-CCONTA
                     , :COCD6800-GDESC
                     , :COCD6800-NINTCNT
                     , :COCD6800-NINTMOV
                     , :COCD6800-NSALDOINI
                     , :COCD6800-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD6800-NSALDOACT
                  FROM  COVT6800
                 WHERE  CIBAN = :COCD6800-CIBAN
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6800 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                   TO COCV9311-CIBAN-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CIBAN-N-EXISTS
                   TO COCV9311-CIBAN-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                   TO COCV9311-CIBAN-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 MOVE COCD6800-NSALDOACT TO WS-NSALDOINI
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2250-TABELA-CONTAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2260-UPDATE-CONTAS
      *-------------------------------------------------------------
       2260-UPDATE-CONTAS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2260-UPDATE-CONTAS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9310-CIBAN        TO COCD6800-CIBAN.
           ADD  1                     TO COCD6800-NINTMOV.
           MOVE COCD6800-NINTMOV      TO WS-NINTMOV.

           EXEC SQL
             UPDATE COVT6800
                SET
                    NINTMOV = :COCD6800-NINTMOV
              WHERE
                    CIBAN = :COCD6800-CIBAN
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6800 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CIBAN-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2260-UPDATE-CONTAS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-INSERE-DADOS.
      *-------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-INSERE-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-INSERE-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9310-NINTCNT         TO COCD6900-NINTCNT.
           MOVE WS-NINTMOV               TO COCD6900-NINTMOV.
           MOVE COCV9310-CTIPOMOV        TO COCD6900-CTIPOMOV.
           MOVE COCV9310-DDATMOV         TO COCD6900-DDATMOV.
           MOVE COCV9310-GREFMOV         TO COCD6900-GREFMOV.
           MOVE COCV9310-DDATVAL         TO COCD6900-DDATVAL.
           MOVE COCV9310-GDESC           TO COCD6900-GDESC.
           MOVE COCV9310-NVALORMOV       TO COCD6900-NVALORMOV.

           COMPUTE COCD6900-NSALDAPM = WS-NSALDOINI +
                                       COCD6900-NVALORMOV.
           MOVE COCD6900-NSALDAPM        TO COCV9311-NSALDAPM.
           MOVE COCD6900-NSALDAPM        TO WS-NSALDOACT.

           MOVE COCK0002-NAO             TO COCD6900-CRECON.
           MOVE SPACES                   TO COCD6900-CCHAVREC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUTILIZA-I      TO COCD6900-CUSERID.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS

           EXEC SQL
                INSERT INTO COVT6900
                (
                   NINTCNT
                 , NINTMOV
                 , CTIPOMOV
                 , DDATMOV
                 , GREFMOV
                 , DDATVAL
                 , GDESC
                 , NVALORMOV
                 , NSALDAPM
                 , CRECON
                 , CCHAVREC
                 , CUSERID
                 , HTIMEST
                )
                VALUES (
                       :COCD6900-NINTCNT
                     , :COCD6900-NINTMOV
                     , :COCD6900-CTIPOMOV
                     , :COCD6900-DDATMOV
                     , :COCD6900-GREFMOV
                     , :COCD6900-DDATVAL
                     , :COCD6900-GDESC
                     , :COCD6900-NVALORMOV
                     , :COCD6900-NSALDAPM
                     , :COCD6900-CRECON
                     , :COCD6900-CCHAVREC
                     , :COCD6900-CUSERID
                     , CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                )
           END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6900 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-DUPREC
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                      MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                        TO COCV9311-CIBAN-S
                      MOVE COCK0001-CIBAN-EXISTS
                        TO COCV9311-CIBAN-MSG
                      MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                        TO COCV9311-CIBAN-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    IF NOT DB2-OK
                       MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                       MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                         TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2399-INSERE-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2500-UPDATE-SALDO
      *-------------------------------------------------------------
       2500-UPDATE-SALDO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2500-UPDATE-SALDO ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9310-CIBAN        TO COCD6800-CIBAN.
           MOVE WS-NSALDOACT          TO COCD6800-NSALDOACT.

           EXEC SQL
             UPDATE COVT6800
                SET
                    NSALDOACT = :COCD6800-NSALDOACT
              WHERE
                    CIBAN = :COCD6800-CIBAN
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6800 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CIBAN-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV9311-CIBAN-CAPLIC
              ELSE
                 IF NOT DB2-OK
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                      TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2
                TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-IF.

       2500-UPDATE-SALDO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV9311-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV9311-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV9311-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
           COPY VIAP0016.
